  source software, and &lt;a
  href=&quot;https://loonwerks.com/people/david-hardin.html&quot;&gt;David Hardin&lt;/a&gt;,
  Associate Director of Systems Engineering at Collins Aerospace, will give
  an overview on trends in real-world formal verification. Details coming soon!
&lt;/p&gt;
